sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User (SDK/UI)
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432/TCP
    participant S3 as Object Store (S3)<br/>9000/TCP
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow<br/>Controller
    participant Driver as Driver (sidecar)
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant Launcher as Launcher (sidecar)
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SWC as Scheduled Workflow<br/>Controller

    Note over User,Launcher: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission and Execution

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>HTTP 8888/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Store run metadata<br/>SQL 3306/5432/TCP<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    API->>S3: Store pipeline spec<br/>HTTP 9000/TCP<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey
    API->>K8s: Submit Argo Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: SA Token
    K8s->>Argo: Watch event (new Workflow)
    Argo->>Driver: Execute driver step<br/>(Pod exec)

    Driver->>MLMD: Resolve inputs, record context<br/>gRPC 8080/TCP<br/>Encryption: Optional TLS
    Driver->>API: Cache lookup (TaskService)<br/>gRPC 8887/TCP<br/>Encryption: Optional TLS

    Argo->>Launcher: Execute launcher in user container<br/>(Pod exec)
    Launcher->>Launcher: Execute user code
    Launcher->>S3: Upload artifacts<br/>HTTP 9000/TCP<br/>Auth: AccessKey/SecretKey
    Launcher->>MLMD: Publish execution results<br/>gRPC 8080/TCP

    Note over User,SWC: Flow 2: Recurring Run Scheduling

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/recurringruns<br/>HTTP 8888/TCP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>K8s: Create ScheduledWorkflow CR<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: SA Token
    SWC->>K8s: Watch ScheduledWorkflow CRs<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: SA Token
    SWC->>API: CreateRun (on schedule trigger)<br/>gRPC 8887/TCP<br/>Auth: Projected SA Token (1h)

    Note over PA,API: Flow 3: Workflow Status Persistence

    PA->>K8s: Watch Argo Workflows<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: SA Token
    PA->>API: ReportWorkflow status<br/>gRPC 8887/TCP<br/>Auth: Projected SA Token (1h)

    Note over K8s,DB: Flow 4: Pipeline Step Caching (Webhook)

    participant Cache as Cache Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    K8s->>Cache: Pod CREATE admission<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP<br/>Auth: K8s client cert
    Cache->>DB: Lookup cache fingerprint<br/>SQL 3306/TCP<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    Cache-->>K8s: AdmissionResponse<br/>(mutate to no-op if cached)
